Introduction

Ayno is a South Korean rapper-songwriter. He is best known for being a member of the boy group VAV. He, along with Lou and Ziu, joined the group in 2017.

Prior to debuting, he participated on the survival show "NO.MERCY" but was ultimately eliminated.

He made his solo debut on March 12, 2024 with the digital single "Good Mistakes".
